Package: dtr
Type: Package
Title: Descriptive Tables with R in the Field of Epidemiology
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author@R: person("Jeremie", "Lespinasse", email = "jeremie.lespinasse@outlook.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")
Description: Quickly inspect grouped data producing descriptive tables. It
    provides several statistics for the entire dataset or groups. Statistical
    comparisons either paramatric or not can be added between groups. Then it
    may render tables in html/pdf with knitr and kableExtra packages or docx
    document with flextable package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    tidyr (>= 0.8.3),
    purrr (>= 0.3.2),
    rlang (>= 0.3.3),
    kableExtra (>= 1.1.0)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    flextable (>= 0.5.4)
